# 🚀 Nisar AI Studio

AI-powered SaaS tool to generate **viral short-form content** for TikTok, YouTube Shorts, and Instagram Reels.

---

## 🔥 What This Does

Generate:
- 5 Viral Hooks
- 3 Content Ideas
- 1 Full Script (30–60 sec)

All in seconds using AI.

---

## 🎯 Target Users

- Content Creators
- Digital Marketers
- AI Entrepreneurs
- Beginners building online income

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- Frontend: HTML + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Vercel Serverless Functions
- AI: OpenAI API

---

## 🚀 Features

- Niche-based content generation
- Multi-platform optimization
- Tone customization (Storytelling, Aggressive, Educational)
- Fast API-based generation

---

